<p>Welcome to the Beta Release of our project inspiration and ideation platform. Our goal is to make it easier for teachers to create authentic projects
 and celebrate students building products, ideas, and their mastery. This is one of the many initiatives from The Da Vinci Institute. The Project Leo platform 
 was built after observing the amazing educators that build the Da Vinci Schools network over the last 15 years and identifying two key insights about
 teaching and learning.</p>

