<h2>The Da Vinci Institute for Professional Learning</h2>
<p><b>The purpose of the Da Vinci Institute for Professional Learning is to help educators prepare students to lead, innovate, and thrive in the modern world.</b><br> 
We do this by creating authentic professional learning experiences that strengthen connections between educators across the Da Vinci Schools and its partners, 
focusing specifically on the following four areas:</p>
<ol>
    <li><b>Organizational Connectedness</b> - facilitating access to the knowledge and experience of colleagues within the Da Vinci organization & network</li>
    <li><b>Professional Learning</b> - growing instructional and leadership capacity within the Da Vinci organization</li>
    <li><b>Connecting Education to Employment</b> - growing instructional and leadership capacity within the Da Vinci organization</li>
    <li><b>Network Development</b> - growing instructional and leadership capacity within the Da Vinci organization</li>
</ol>



